{"tid":1488047,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"同我入嚟！如何正確經濟攬炒","createTime":"2019-08-19T13:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T15:13:49.000Z","uid":291203,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cd2323e62ce609f7887c63422bac5758a1416e9b","tid":1488047,"uid":291203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:34:57.000Z","msg":"［代朋友post］<br />\n<br />\n某d中資公司每月銷售數據已經出咗嚟，七月份數據俾五、六月低左近50%。大陸果班人頭豬都不知幾驚，一來無錢搵，二來又少左機會俾佢走資，仲請少咗好多人（大陸落嚟香港讀書嘅畢業生） <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但大家唔好咁開心住，點解？</span><br />\n<br />\n因為中國佬最叻就係趁火打劫，大家睇吓<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>國泰</strong></span>同<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>匯豐</strong></span>，就知道人哋其實想趁亂做低你個股價，在將港資公司全部染紅。染紅之後，你嘅所有個人資料，包括電話數據，購物紀錄，一舉一動佢哋都會掌握係手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（現階段已有好多港股，最大股東都係一啲不知名嘅所謂投資公司控制，其實後面都係中共。）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>而中共嘅目標係，有朝一日揸乾晒香港啲錢，俾深圳成為最大贏家，人哋點推廣深圳，都唔代表會放棄香港呢個走資港㗎 ！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只要一日中共仲有錢，佢都會想盡辦法將香港人所有日常生活品、消費品都染紅。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">明顯地，你哋班仆街咁得唔夠多錢啊！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">銀行個利息一日唔夠高，但中資佬就繼續借錢再借錢，去買你哋啲股票啦！</span><br />\n<br />\n仲有呀！你哋買乜都好，都唔好用中資。女仔唔該你哋買少件衫啦！好多都中國入口製造！買少啲淘寶啦仆街！買太空卡，都唔好用中字頭嗰啲呀！去旅行唔好上CTrip，貴少少，又算得係乜？食野就咪再食金拱門！<br />\n<br />\n屌你地班仆街，有良心企業就盡情掃貨，多啲課㗎啦！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後最後，你地真係禁唔夠錢啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋要認清目標，只炒中資公司，不炒良心企業。咁先係香港人想要既攬炒呀！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"16e133cd2bb5bf19152452b72fd909e4f129e111","tid":1488047,"uid":291203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:39:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a85f35dd55aebd7b2735458795c3234e49e8a3bb","tid":1488047,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70151d405aa007ebd150559f3c40caeaf8c312f","tid":1488047,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:43:07.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8d610b11476bf8b27c3d1ad9c8d355de0883af4b","tid":1488047,"uid":291203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a85f35dd55aebd7b2735458795c3234e49e8a3bb","tid":1488047,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6b174051e462666c0d568d4228d362d7663956","tid":1488047,"uid":254361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:48:11.000Z",